{"article_id":"jQRooGkoSwGLte8I","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama on Tuesday praised a bipartisan Senate effort","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to overhaul the US immigration system","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he ' d wait for Congress to take the lead on this issue .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"\" At this moment , it looks like there is a genuine desire","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to get this done soon ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and that ' s very encouraging , \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Obama said in what officials billed as a major speech on the subject in Las Vegas .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"But the president indicated","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that his patience is provisional .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"He laid out principles","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"should be reflected in any comprehensive immigration-reform legislation ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and he said","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"if lawmakers get bogged down bickering ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"he ' ll act .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"\" If Congress is unable to move forward in a timely fashion ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"I will send up a bill","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"based on my proposal","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and insist","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"they vote on it right away , \"","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Obama seemed to be trying to accomplish the difficult feat","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"of appearing to exert presidential leadership","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"while letting a rare moment of bipartisanship bloom .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"He probably knows","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"if he demands certain details right now ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"he ' ll polarize the situation","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and make it harder for lawmakers to come together .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner ' s response to the speech hinted at how that dynamic might play out .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"\" There are a lot of ideas","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"about how best to fix our broken immigration system , \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"said Boehner spokesman Brendan Buck .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" Any solution should be a bipartisan one ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and we hope","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"the president is careful not to drag the debate to the left","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and ultimately disrupt the difficult work","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that is ahead in the House and Senate . \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Given that response , it ' s difficult to see how a White House-drafted bill would make any progress in the GOP-dominated House ,","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"should the current congressional effort languish .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"As with the bipartisan Senate approach","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"announced Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Obama says","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"he wants immigration reform to reflect strengthened border security , a path to citizenship for many of the estimated 11 million illegal immigrants currently in the US , and a crackdown on employers","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"who hire undocumented workers .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Unlike the Senate effort , Obama would not condition the citizenship process on further security efforts .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"He would move immediately to allow undocumented workers to register ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"pass a background check ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"pay taxes and a fine ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"and then qualify for a probationary legal status .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"\" Individuals must wait","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"until the existing legal immigration backlogs are cleared","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"before getting in line","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"to apply for lawful permanent residency","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"( i.e . a ' green card ' ) ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and ultimately United States citizenship , \"","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"according to a White House fact sheet .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"This might take some time for the individuals involved ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Obama said on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"\" It won ' t be a quick process ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"but it will be a fair process ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and it will lift these individuals out of the shadows , \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"he said in Las Vegas .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"According to the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"the administration is proposing mandatory , phased-in electronic employment verification .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"For most employers , use of the current E-Verify immigration-status system is largely voluntary .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Obama is also pushing use of fraud- and tamper-resistant Social Security cards and other documents","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"to prove immigration status .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"In the past , proposals for a national identity card have proved controversial in Congress ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"to say the least .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"Unlike the Senate effort , Obama ' s plan would treat same-sex immigrant couples the same as heterosexual couples for the purpose of family reunification .","depth":3},{"id":78,"text":"It would also create a \" start-up visa , \"","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"allowing entrepreneurs with established financing to locate in the US .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"\" If you succeed ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"you ' ll create American businesses , and American jobs , \"","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"said Obama .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":165,"left":154,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":124,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":105,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":90,"right":104,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":90,"left":86,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":84,"right":85,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":84,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":88,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":87,"right":6,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":91,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":93,"right":102,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":10,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":96,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":13,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":14,"right":94,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":17,"right":99,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration